<p>The post <a href="https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/discussion/using-technology-to-treat-parkinsons-inside-neurodegenerative-movement-disorders-video/">Using technology to treat Parkinson&amp;#8217;s: Inside neurodegenerative movement disorders (VIDEO)</a> appeared first on <a href="https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org">Mayo Clinic News Network</a>.</p>
