<mayoclinic:mcimg16x9>https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/n7-mcnn/7bcc9724adf7b803/uploads/2026/04/Researchers-GettyImages-16x9-1.jpg</mayoclinic:mcimg16x9>
