<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Terri Malloy, Mayo Clinic Communications,&amp;nbsp;<a href="mailto:newsbureau@mayo.edu" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">newsbureau@mayo.edu</a></li>
</ul>
